title: Fans brave rain for new Apple iPhones - Iol.co.za
text:
A customer receives his phone as Apple iPhone 6s and 6s Plus go on sale at an Apple Store in Beijing on September 25, 2015. Picture: Damir Sagolj Sydney/San Francisco - The new iPhone 6s and 6s Plus hit stores on Friday, with dozens of people - and a robot - queueing in Sydney to kick off a global sales cycle that will be scrutinised for signs of how much juice Apple Inc's marquee product has left.
 Iol.co.za.
